<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-48-0871 </DOCNO><TEXT>This patent describes a method of solidifying a radioactive or hazardousliquid comprising at least about 95% water by adding only sodium montmorillonitehaving a major portion of particles between about 3/8 inch and 20 meshthereto in a sodium montmorillonite:-liquid ratio of between about 1:2and about 1:7, respectively, in fractions with at least a few minutesinterval between fractions, until the composition comprises an unpourable,free standing solid.</TEXT></DOC>